c 002 24 DemoCircleSlot 229 435 65 65 1 
c 003 24 DemoSquareSlot 328 435 65 65 1 
c 004 24 DemoTriangleSlot 427 435 65 65 1 
c 005 4 MatchHint 110 538 500 32 1 BECOME THE SHAPE BEFORE IT HITS YOU
c 006 4 SectionDodge 160 640 400 40 1 2. DODGE LANES
c 007 4 DodgeHintDesktop 110 710 500 32 1 USE LEFT / RIGHT ARROW KEYS
c 008 4 DodgeHintWeb 110 710 500 32 1 SWIPE LEFT OR RIGHT
c 009 4 SectionEnergy 160 806 400 40 1 3. KEEP YOUR ENERGY
c 010 4 EnergyHint 110 877 500 32 1 MISSES DRAIN THE BAR ON THE LEFT
c 011 4 ClearHint 110 973 500 32 1 CLEAR A SONG TO SET A HIGH SCORE
c 012 5 ContinueButton 180 1075 360 102 1 START
